I am a gamer. Extensive history with using the Hidden Modifier (HD Mod for short) and I am also very comfortable with EZ (Easy Modifier). In all seriousness I'm a long time tournament veteran (since 2017) and a HD/EZ specialist. I have many notable scores using both mods as well as some highly contested leaderboard spots with the EZ mod. On top of being a low AR specialist. I am also a solid consistency player and I am pretty good with HDHR as well. What I'm NOT good at is high bpm (anything > 260 bpm) and high AR (anything > AR 10.3). I will genuinely struggle and or bottom score the lobby if I have to play a DT map that is too fast or too high AR.
